premise_source_doc_sentence: Shallow Hal is a 2001 American romantic comedy film starring Gwyneth Paltrow and Jack Black about a shallow man who falls in love with an overweight woman .

He is known for his roles in High Fidelity  (  2000  )  , Shallow Hal  (  2001  )  , School of Rock  (  2003  )  , King Kong  (  2005  )  , The Holiday  (  2006  )  , Nacho Libre  (  2006  )  , Kung Fu Panda  (  2008  )  , Tropic Thunder  (  2008  )  , Gulliver 's Travels  (  2010  )  , Kung Fu Panda 2  (  2011  )  , Bernie  (  2011  )  , Goosebumps  (  2015  )  , and Kung Fu Panda 3  (  2016  )  .
